Text:
They've had some bad hosts in recent years,
but they don't get any worse than Justin Bieber!
It could be worse... Adam Levine could have co-hosted and then the two of them did sketches together...

The writing wasn't so hot last night either, but as far as hosts go, next week's SNL will be great with Christophe Waltz !  A true actor adept in either comedy or drama ( see the last two Tarentino films).

How about Carrie Brownstein from "Portlandia" for the season finale?  She and Fred Armisen work so well together.
TY for the upload, lotta Beiber jealousy in the comments so far. Guys you are here, you obv. came here to download this, your outing yourself by leaving a comment!
